videos.headline: Shimonek scrambles and throws for TD
videos.description: Nic Shimonek buys his receiver, Cameron Batson, time and connects on a nine-yard touchdown to get Texas Tech on the board early.

videos.headline: Mayfield answers back with first TD
videos.description: Baker Mayfield connects with CeeDee Lamb on a 24-yard touchdown to tie the game for the Sooners.

videos.headline: Adams breaks into Texas Tech territory with huge gain
videos.description: Abdul Adams gets outside for a big 35-yard run for the Sooners.

videos.headline: Flowers crashes in for the Sooner TD
videos.description: Dimitri Flowers converts the one-yard touchdown on the ground to put Oklahoma up 14-13.

videos.headline: Brown finds space for Oklahoma TD
videos.description: Baker Mayfield connects with the speedy Marquise Brown for a three-yard touchdown to give the Sooners the lead.

videos.headline: Anderson takes in another Sooner TD
videos.description: Rodney Anderson gets his turn with a five-yard touchdown increasing Oklahoma's lead to 28-20.

videos.headline: Oklahoma opens the 3rd quarter with quick TD
videos.description: Baker Mayfield drives the Sooners down the field in 72 seconds, capping off the drive with a one-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Batson bobbles and scores TD for Texas Tech
videos.description: Cameron Batson juggles a 9-yard touchdown catch from Nic Shimonek as he dives into the end zone for the Red Raiders.

videos.headline: Andrews holds on for Oklahoma's sixth TD
videos.description: Baker Mayfield finds Mark Andrews for a seven-yard touchdown pass that would be confirmed after review.

videos.headline: Sooner Schooner breaks down
videos.description: The Sooner Schooner has trouble completing its touchdown celebration and needs some assistance getting back into the tunnel.

videos.headline: Lamb gets hit hard on TD catch
videos.description: CeeDee Lamb takes a targeting hit on a 14-yard touchdown pass from Baker Mayfield padding Oklahoma's lead.

videos.headline: Mayfield: 'Knew our backs were against the wall'
videos.description: Oklahoma quarterback Baker Mayfield talks about how his team's win against Texas Tech was crucial for their conference hopes.

videos.headline: Mayfield puts on another masterful performance
videos.description: Steve Levy and Brian Griese discuss the high-scoring game between Oklahoma and Texas Tech and the weapons Baker Mayfield has in his arsenal.

videos.headline: Oklahoma rolls over Texas Tech
videos.description: Baker Mayfield throws four touchdowns in the Sooners' 49-27 win over Texas Tech.
